a.xlink:title: Supports mapping from names to handles and vice-versa for a module, window, function, or attribute.
A Function object corresponds to a function member of a window.
A DataItem object is a data member of a window.
A ComponentInterface object contains multiple panes and multiple data dataitems.
A Pane object contains a mesh, pane dataitem, and field variables.
Encapsulates an element-connectivity of a mesh.
